Pro golfer Grayson Murray is a 23-year-old rookie hoping to qualify for the Masters tournament—which obviously isn’t easy. But now he’s got a whole lot of motivation to make it to Augusta, Georgia on April 6. Playboy model Lindsey Pelas could be his caddie. 2
